[ProMED thanks Dr Nicole Berens-Riha for this
report. We believe that this is the 1st report of
_P. knowlesi_ from Indonesia, but as she points
out, it was expected to find human cases of _P.
knowlesi_ in Indonesian Borneo after they had
been described in Malaysian Borneo. - Mod.EP]
